                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1913-1 淡水中學白話字史料(修編) 文類-選擇文類 作者--/-]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12229.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(24)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12229.htm">十個故事 [ Cha̍p--ê kò͘-sū ]</a></span>
