            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-10 芥菜子 文類-選擇文類 作者--/-]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12209.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(2)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12209.htm">怎樣用聖經 [ CHÁI-IŪN ĒNG SÈNG-KENG ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">怎樣用聖經



憂悶&ecirc;時 
讀 
約翰14:


失志&ecirc;時
"
詩篇27:


犯罪&ecirc;時
" 
詩篇51:


煩惱&ecirc;時 
" 
馬太6: 19-34.


危險&ecirc;時
" 
詩篇91:


受逼&ecirc;時
<span s...<a href="artical-12209.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="white" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/4baac7bb24f9a.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/4baac7bb24f9a.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-10 芥菜子 文類-詩 作者--/-]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12210.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(2)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12210.htm">我Ê花園（白話詩） [ GOÁ Ê HOE-HN̂G (pe̍h-oē-si) ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">我&Ecirc;花園（白話詩）
1.    我&ecirc;花園真正媠，草木青翠花大蕊，亦有山仔kap涼亭，清&ecirc;埤仔kap p&ucirc;n水。
2.   樹眉ē花真正芳，牡丹、茶花真正紅，百合、茉莉色真白，含笑、玉蘭真大叢。
3.   春天我來遮行遊，O-ia̍h會k&oacute;e心憂愁，夏天我來遮休憩，規陣&ecirc;蟬叫l&egrave;-l&egrave;。
4.   秋天我來遮散步，火金姑點燈chhōa路；冬天我來遮觀景，雖然酸風也袂冷。
5.   我若身軀有厭siān,蜜蜂送蜜真利便，我若心神有煩惱，媠花安慰真拄好。
6.    柑桔、桃李，kap蘋...<a href="artical-12210.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="#fffff9" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/4baac82208838.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/4baac82208838.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-10 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者--/-]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12212.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(3)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12212.htm">教會自養 [ KÀU-HOĒ CHŪ-IÓNG ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">教會自養
　　教會自養，就是自然應盡&ecirc;天職。台灣教會建設到taⁿ有60外年，若無進行到自養&ecirc;日，實在真見笑，也是無盡基督徒&ecirc;本份。若欲做純萃&ecirc;台灣基督教會，tio̍h有家己自養自立；親像人到長成，的確著有自養，thang建立家庭；毋thang koh倚靠父母。咱毋thang干但專倚靠母會teh幫贊，著有自養&ecirc;精神chiah合宜。&Agrave;i欲自養，要緊著有3項：－
　　1.      培養人才。教會欲得著自養，要緊財政著有夠額。財政是對佇會友&ecirc;事業kap程度&ecirc;增差thang得著。會友&ecirc;程度...<a href="artical-12212.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="white" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/4baac5fa486fb.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/4baac5fa486fb.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-10 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者--/-]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12216.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(3)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12216.htm">慈愛Ê結子（聖誕è故事） [ CHÛ-ÀI Ê KIAT-CHÍ (Sèng-tàn è kò͘-sū) ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">慈愛&Ecirc;結子（聖誕&egrave;故事）
　　「玫瑰花、玫瑰花，啥人欲買我&ecirc;玫瑰花？」一个媠媠&ecirc;查某囡仔，發出輕輕細細&ecirc;聲；穿真破&ecirc;衫褲，用軟弱&ecirc;手捾一跤破籃，t&eacute;濟濟欲謝欲謝&ecirc;花，看伊瘦瘦&ecirc;面，kap兩支路糊糜&ecirc;跤，就知伊是喪鄉失調養，無得著快樂趣味--&ecirc;。徛佇路邊teh閃避青冷&ecirc;北風。街路&ecirc;人穿長袍皮裘，尚且teh叫koaⁿ-&aacute;！koaⁿ-&aacute;！若是。這个查某囡仔予無情&ecirc;冷風吹到gī-gī-chh...<a href="artical-12216.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="#fffff9" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
